name: Payal & Aditya
body:
Our Wedding
=======

## Long Story Short

1. 1986, He was born in New Delhi
1. 1987, She was born in some obscure part of India
1. Time goes on <_...queue romantic music_>
1. They meet through friends some time in 2006. Go on dates <..._yawn_ _blah, blah, blah_>
1. One day, that he totally remembers but is not willing to divulge, He says "Will You?", she says some version of "Yes!"
  * _drumroll_
  * **Aditya** & **Payal** are getting married
  * _applause_

## Save the date

### 14th December, 2014
#### Somewhere in New Delhi, India
